re. They have literally just held her largest illegal gathering in their history. As we speak they are calling for a horological revolution in our time. They have held laser pointers to the skies and tried to to impossibly set alight the stars. I cannot help be proud of them, to cry for them, and to lament their pain&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n淨係睇呢段已經眼濕濕<br />\n今年佢篇致謝詞如果又寫得咁好 分分鐘真係中完又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de75755ab2f92977ee4b7a3f4e08d9048157c3af","tid":2137424,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:44:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}